{"tid":1552300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係應承左點都唔割，點都唔篤灰咩？","createTime":"2019-09-08T10:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T14:57:25.000Z","uid":132497,"like":92,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"fb323598c2227286651993cb54faa43b541c2328","tid":1552300,"uid":132497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:05:44.000Z","msg":"無錯，可能你地覺得前線點解今日都要搞<br />\n無錯，可能你地覺得今日應該係和理非請願<br />\n<br />\n事實係前線今日已經做左野，無得改變<br />\n咁我地後勤唔係應該諗下點樣去加大文宣力度去返美領請願，或者解釋點解前線會有行動咩（e.g. 想幫831受害者，中環和平集會都俾警犬挑釁，etc）？<br />\n<br />\n你今日割得或者想割，你就唔好再話核爆都唔割<br />\n宜家又無人搞美領，你懷疑係鬼做你就自己走去問，走去解釋俾前線聽今日點解唔好咁近美領周邊有衝突<br />\n唔想上身嘅，或者冷氣軍師嘅，就諗下點樣集中做英文文宣去解釋俾國際聽今日集會目的，或者幫下前線解釋佢地行動嘅目的，而唔係花精神去屌自己友<br />\n<br />\nYes. You may wonder why the frontlines are taking actions today<br />\nYes. You think today should be a peaceful protest.<br />\n<br />\nThe truth is, things have already happened and you can't change that.<br />\nSo rather than blaming those frontiline, we should focus on explaining why we have this petition to US consulate or why the frontline takes action today (e.g. helping the victims of 831 incident, being provoked by police despite of being in an approved peaceful assembly)?<br />\n<br />\nIf you wanna cut tie or think of cutting tie with frontline today, please don't say &quot;Not even a nuclear holocaust can divide us&quot;<br />\nNo one has taken any actions toward or around US consulate. If you suspect they are undercover cop, please go ahead to ask them or explain why today is not appropriate to take actions near US consulate.<br />\nIf you don't want to get close to them or are staying at home, please help explain to the world why we are having this assembly and petition in US consulate today, or why the frontline is taking action. BUT PLEASE DON'T WASTE YOUR TIME TO JUDGE OUR TEAMMATES<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">核爆都唔割</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d728a1a406ae9d6a347a81ca61a6d25bdfdf9775","tid":1552300,"uid":132497,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:06:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>核爆都唔割</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"bd8742059f05d5db2b3c420f55d554cc75d3c0f4","tid":1552300,"uid":132497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:07:06.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割"},{"pid":"f9fe38232177f93ca0a6e5e963f396a5509e397a","tid":1552300,"uid":196450,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:07:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">殺人放火燒香港我都唔撚柒割！！！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5e4cabe9968696454b34116b211b86a5879bf594","tid":1552300,"uid":41818,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:07:14.000Z","msg":"機場事件2.0 你幫我執屎係應份"},{"pid":"fa3bf6122e3cf28544b1bb32756068f44f7d2d3b","tid":1552300,"uid":132497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:07:16.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割"},{"pid":"94296aa9a4fef49c4ac79443c518cade2be4382e","tid":1552300,"uid":132497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:07:29.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割"},{"pid":"ece172be510f460e7afe0defe70d8c43d0f8faca","tid":1552300,"uid":120431,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f42f2ae61bb8e0d35c4fa45e3c6400d538f125","tid":1552300,"uid":132497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:07:43.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割"},{"pid":"e29d52928937e014b120abe5a50eb476d92ca5cd","tid":1552300,"uid":132497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:07:55.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割"},{"pid":"2bdf85fb368e58cfc4343c38ecc217ff2cec1299","tid":1552300,"uid":287116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:08:00.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割！"},{"pid":"05b62bed8fa16f6b3e496290314032b271